  "description": {
    "de": "Hugne, der Gedächtnislose, besaß einst eine wunderschöne Kristallkugel, die er von seinem Großvater geerbt hatte. Da er sie zur Erinnerung stets bei sich tragen wollte, befestigte er sie an der Spitze seines Hutes, auf dass sie ihn immer begleiten würde... Doch dann vergaß er sie und starb an Erschöpfung beim Versuch, sie wiederzufinden.",
    "en": "Hung 'Short Memory' Lekahurse owned a magnificent crystal ball - his grandpa gave it to him. He wisely decided to hold on to it for the rest of his life. In fact, he put it on his hat which he never took off again, until one day, a jealous breeze took it away. He followed, and the breeze seemed to mock him, suspending the hat in the air, and whipping it away just as his searching fist approached. Not without a sense of decency, the wind took him home for a brief visit once a season and when it sensed the poor man was close to the end, took him to the edge of a cliff, hung the hat there for a moment and down Lekahurse tumbled, at peace at last.",
    "es": "Hugne, «el sin memoria», poseía una bola de crystal que le había regalado su abuelito. Ya que estaba decidido a conservarla toda su vida, la colocó sobre un sombrero que no se quitaba nunca... Y murió de cansancio intentando encontrarla.",
    "fr": "Hugne \"le sans mémoire\" possédait une magnifique boule de crystal que lui avait donné son pépé. Bien décidé à la conserver toute sa vie, il la plaça sur son chapeau, qu'il ne quittait jamais... Il est mort de fatigue, en essayant de la retrouver.",
    "id": "48910",
    "pt": "Hugne ‘Memória Curta‘ possuiu uma magnífica bola de cristal, que seu vovô havia lhe dado. Bem decidido mantê-la pelo resto de sua vida, ele a pôs no chapéu que nunca tirava... Ela foi tão bem guardada, que ele morreu de fadiga tentando encontrá-la."
  },
